{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join our Discord  Or ELSE!....Or else you'll miss out on updates, competitions and having a big impact on this project...\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459070/extras/FadeTwitterNew-1-NPCDialogueClipVincentGaillard-5.gif?t=1734125672\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>FADE</strong> is an <strong>Dark Fantasy Action RPG</strong> that combines combat inspired by the <strong>\u201cSouls Series\u201d</strong> with the narrative direction of <strong>FABLE</strong> and the anime <strong>Full Metal Alchemist</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459070/extras/FadeKickstarterTrailerProttype-13.gif?t=1734125672\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <strong>FADE</strong> players will be tasked with exploring the settlements of <strong>Celeste, Solemn, Whisper, and The Baltane Capital</strong> in order stop the <strong>5 Homunculus Monarchs</strong>, each with their own unique spin on alchemy and combat, sharing a destructive plot to sacrifice the country.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To succeed in your journey you'll have to, take on side quests, craft useful items and collect powerful equipment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459070/extras/374-3747135_terminator-board-game-live-on-kickstarter.png?t=1734125672\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459070/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734125672","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459070/page.bg.jpg?t=1734125672","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/14590